  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>Alstern Marine & Offshore Pte Ltd was founded in 2011. Our business scope involves distributing Sealxpert pipeline maintenance, repair & overhaul products to customers in the Oil & Gas, Petrochemical, Chemical, Power, Water Utilities and Facilities Management Industries. Currently, our products are distributed to more than 35 countries worldwide in Asia, Middle East, Europe, America and Australia.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking an Admin Assistant to support daily operations by preparing items for delivery and handling basic documentation tasks in our Ubi area office.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Pick and pack items accurately to prepare orders for timely delivery to customers</li><li>Complete basic documentation tasks to support order processing and maintain accurate records</li><li>Communicate clearly in English to coordinate with team members and ensure smooth workflow</li><li>Use basic computer skills to perform administrative duties and enter data efficiently</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Basic computer skills to support documentation and communication tasks</li><li>Ability to communicate, read, and write in English to ensure effective teamwork and accurate documentation</li><li>Knowledge of Autocount and MYOB software as an added advantage</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Location: Ubi area (near Macpherson / Ubi MRT)</li><li>Working hours: Monday to Friday: 8:30am – 6:00pm;1 rotational Saturday morning (8:30am – 1:00pm) every 1–1.5 months; <em>During probation: alternate Saturdays</em></li><li>Interested applicants: Please WhatsApp or call (65) 9880 0335</li></ul>",
